Publisher: Pierre Mariette le fils (French, Paris 1634–1716 Paris)
Heilbrunn Timeline of Art History: French Decorative Arts during the Reign of Louis XIV (1654–1715)
Description: This print is bound in Volume IV of Oeuvres.  Jombert published his collection of Le Pautre in 1751. Volume IV contains "desseins d'ornemens et trophées d'armes;" This print is part of a series of six plates depicting ornament for panels.  The series was published by Pierre II Mariette and was republished by Jombert in 1751.
